\[  ] This section is being filled by a representative of the court.
\[  ] This section is being filled by the witness themselves.
\[  ] This affidavit was written while the witness was in a safe location
\[  ] The boxes in the affidavit were written in by the witness, and only the witness.
\[  ] Before signing this document, this document was not in the custody of an unathorized holder
